urchased items before September. If you purchased items before September, ...\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Steven Zahm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1471:\"<p>Back in September the eshop / cart was upgraded to bring you easier access to your past purchases and free updates via your &#8220;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;. Since September the old and new eshop/carts were running so access could still could be provided to everyone who had purchased items before September.</p><p>If you purchased items before September, over the past two days, your account has been migrated to the new eshop/cart. This migration triggered an email invoice for your past purchases which provides the details of your order, the download links and a link to your &#8220;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;. <strong>There are <em>no</em> additional charges or fees associated with your account migration</strong>. The old eshop/cart has been discontinued and removed. The download link and code you received with your original order will no longer function as of today. Please access your purchases from your &#8221;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;.</p><p>I thank you in advance for your understanding and patience. Happy New Years to you and yours!</p> <img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-pro/news/~4/I-RYKsc1TFI\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>