gories without taking up huge amount of screen space while being very user friendly. I&#8217;ve updated the <a href=\"http://connections-pro.com/demo/form/\" title=\"Connections Form Demo\">demo</a>, go give it a spin!</p><div class=\"wp_syntax\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre class=\"php\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color: #666666; font-style: italic;\">/*\n * Example 1\n * Change the default entry type\n */</span>\n<span style=\"color: #009900;\">&#91;</span>connections_form default_type<span style=\"color: #339933;\">=</span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">\'organization\'</span><span style=\"color: #009900;\">&#93;</span>\n&nbsp;\n<span style=\"color: #666666; font-style: italic;\">/*\n * Example 2\n * Disable the Category data type\n */</span>\n<span style=\"color: #009900;\">&#91;</span>connections_form category<span style=\"color: #339933;\">=</span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">\'false\'</span><span style=\"color: #009900;\">&#93;</span></pre></td></tr></table></div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-pro-modules/~4/r0SPIk8X1QM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/04/01/pro-module-update-form-0-2/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/04/01/pro-module-update-form-0-2/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml